<title>当哈佛刘亦婷被吐槽沦为美国中产时，寒门清华女孩上了热搜</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/SuoEiSdqPH</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/SuoEiSdqPH</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;415&quot; data-backw=&quot;622&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/s3CiapicMr8tLMPIWsoYXdEPzcnCmCfkkIfsj6wCvJxDZ2gI5RUGLNibcpyxla8uwwj85IdbbHialNv8pDic8QDV3ZQ/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6666666666666666&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/s3CiapicMr8tLMPIWsoYXdEPzcnCmCfkkIfsj6wCvJxDZ2gI5RUGLNibcpyxla8uwwj85IdbbHialNv8pDic8QDV3ZQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;720&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;20年前被大众看好的哈佛女孩刘亦婷，&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20年后沦为普通美国中产？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;是选择错误？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;还是美式教育毁了她？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;前&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;几天，清华寒门女孩张薇在毕业典礼时的致辞，传遍网络。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;保送清华研究生后，她选择延迟一年入学去支教，用一年时间去做一件终生难忘的事。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一番朴实无华、意义深远的话，让人深思。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;她的选择令人钦佩。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;听从内心的感召，跟从理想&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;，&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;不是每个人都能做出这样的选择&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5576407506702413&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYwRiaOv0TEORj3tySRnPOYRewwibWTcfaic3IibtO2fqLCBRSwnP3JiaNb99A/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;746&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;她在致辞中问到：“&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;你被生活的波涛所淹没了吗？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;她说：“&lt;strong&gt;在万千的选择面前，他们放弃了万人眼中的最优解，跳出了生活的舒适区，走向了祖国最需要的地方。&lt;/strong&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;而她自己也选择成为这样的人。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5533333333333333&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYwSQ7p3FibyQANYs3bB3kLP529rhJM9UoxY1YHia9PTazyQ76kTODwIK5w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;750&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;还记得哈佛女孩刘亦婷吗？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;同样是一个学霸级女生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;20年前，她和韩寒齐名。曾经同上一档叫《对话》的节目，从此两人时常被拿来对比。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一个离经叛道，不被看好；一个“三好学生”，被万千吹捧。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.77079107505071&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYwQsI9KYw0xdmolQUtGmCdYX5XCoKMlvRd1qCTbia6PubuY0hLUaU0bIg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;493&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：网络&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;而如今，人们再度拿两人相比。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;多数人眼中，韩寒功成名就。虽然不再提笔，但仍然是桀骜不羁的“少年”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYwhzp8IpL09WaiaE4MvoQ9gY2njDpMO9IkxRTuMxoLBaPekicOdgdxicBHw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;440&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;567&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.01447178002894356&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYw9LbIOGmiccUUxa2bxYqMfbibcDLAL0DutxbPDLqvmCia0KmsmarTLrGiag/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;691&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：微博&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;写作、出版杂志、赛车、导演……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;他的人生丰富、自由，是无数人想要却复刻不了的生活。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYwAj1dib7WzRAFaejr4fZib72zvqn33FLiczd1EuFPrPoj2Gea3PxrcBpNQ/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;689.9999999999999&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;255.32110091743115&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;716.3761467889908&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6681159420289855&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYwLEG25a11sLlh4KPsN9bq3TT1k6TCg8TicrbE70fic9hUibhr90xF7pKsQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;690&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：韩寒微博&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;而曾经被拿来与韩寒对比，“一个天上，一个地下”的哈佛女孩刘亦婷，在人们眼中却沦为了无名的美国中产。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;622&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;95&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.16193181818181818&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCFuNfAAjk6rQ39Az4tPMYwULyld0noIwZuJLD1FPM4jSial0VbFiaryKQnqg14XLmE92enYQFGSfDA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;704&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;说起刘亦婷，还要从一本书说起。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;当年被各家父母捧在手中的教育典籍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;《哈佛女孩刘亦婷》&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;，将刘亦婷这个名字带入更多大众的视野。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;上哈佛已经让人艳羡不得，被全额奖学金保送哈佛，这份殊荣放在今天也可以出本教育书，何况放在20年前。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;刘亦婷理所当然的成为了那个年代里，最优秀的“别人家的孩子”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;而刘亦婷的父母，也因地适宜，写书出版了教育宝典。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

